Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:04.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I've prepared this. A total of 1,000,000 Yen. {9000 Usd}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.41,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You've helped me out before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:10.84,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying I'm returning the favour,\N but I want you to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.82,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As long as it’s in your hands, \NI'm sure you can earn enough through gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.62,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:21.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Even after such a crushing defeat you're still believing in me and placing your bets on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.48,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But I have no need for this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.01,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, the Student Council hasn't come to collect anything from me as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's why I still have some money on hand right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What? That can’t be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:40.50,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The Student Council being merciless when it comes to debts is common knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:42.95,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I wonder why, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:47.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ah! I’m not certain if it's meant as a replacement, \Nbut this was handed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:50.45,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A Life Plan Form?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yomotsuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:31.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yomotsuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.11,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:37.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Second Year, Flower Class  \Nsaotome Mary-san is asking for an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:41.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ugh... The president isn't here right now, \Nso I guess I’ll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.41,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Saotome-san, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:52.21,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Need something? \NI'm pretty busy right now, so keep it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:56.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This morning I received this \Nright here from the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:01.45,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this ridiculous text?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huuh? Exactly what's written there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.64,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.64,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just what is this creepy text even?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's exactly as it's written there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Everything in there's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.70,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yay, clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:27.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're lucky! \Na diet member's wife, it says!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:35.12,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Still, ‘Orida’ is a filthy \Nold pedo so I'd totally pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:39.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But he has a lot of connections and plenty of funds, so it should work out for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.43,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's already been arranged anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:46.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh? ‘It’s already been arranged’?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's all done and decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:55.68,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's true that this school has \Nstrong connections to political circles, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:58.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Assuming that this is all true, why am I getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd marry just some guy I d–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Your opinion doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:09.04,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of ways to force people to do what they need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.37,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Don't bullshit me! {I like it}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:15.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Who'd even abide by something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.92,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Then pay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.60,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yiha! If you can't pay us back, it’ll all happen for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:28.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just do your best and brush up on your man-pleasing skills, ‘kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:36.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Marriage... Birth... \Nwhat kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:42.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This academy truly \Nnever fails to entertain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Your entire life, down to your marriage partner, is decided by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:53.43,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This livestock status will truly haunt you until you die, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:56.02,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, this is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,When the Student Council says they’ll do something, they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:04.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,True. If I can't return the 300,000,000 Yen \NI'll truly become cattle. {2,700,000 Usd}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Discord, anxiety, anger and despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:11.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Even that familiar classroom is warped by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.42,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This sensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I can't get enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.11,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oi, Jabami Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:23.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You became a Mike, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Kiwatari from the Camellia Class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's quite alright. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We’ve moved quite the distance, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:44.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,So, in what way might I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Take off your clothes. Strip for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Shit, what are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ah, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.16,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,that you were planning to violate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:14.16,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh? I never went that far. \Njust hurry up and strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have to decline after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.62,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Showing my bare skin to strangers is rather unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And also, you gentlemen are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.88,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,a far cry from my preferred type.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:36.43,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Fine, you bitch. \NI’ll violate you, like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Whoa there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just be quiet and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.57,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oi... \Nwhat are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.66,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.41,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.95,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's the Student Council member and head of the beautification committee, Ikishima Midari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:05.14,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can’t just force yourself on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:08.55,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As the head of the beautification committee I should stop that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:13.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If you’re that pent up, I can take care of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.64,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Still, it won’t be for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:23.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We'll decide this with gambling, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.66,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There's only one bullet in the chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:33.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If I pull the trigger and nothing happens, \Nyou can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:38.62,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If it does come out, you’ll just get riddled with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What do you say? Sounds fun, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:48.21,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I don’t get you! \Nare you really this scared of being shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:54.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's a five-in-six chance; if our positions were reversed I'd accept, no questions asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Reversed? That's it! Reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.27,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:06.27,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If no bullet comes out be nice and go back. \NIf it comes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.94,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I probably wouldn't have it in me to resist anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:12.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,so you could just do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:16.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There are absolutely no negatives for you, \Nyou couldn't ask for better conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:19.29,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Anyone would agree that shooting’s the only option!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now, shoot! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.29,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:27.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What are you even saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.09,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm beat, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:42.02,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Why are you leaving? Show some guts! \Nare you not up for it or somethin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:47.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Suzui-san... Yes, I'm quite alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.53,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ikishima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:59.96,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I won't forget my debt to you. \NI'll be sure to repay you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:05.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Don't you think there's something wrong with that girl's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The Student Council seems to be full of weirdos, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,True, this isn't a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,But thanks to those guys, \Nwe can turn a profit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:19.14,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We have to be grateful for that, don’t we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.60,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Shitheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.64,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Fucking teasing bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.70,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Fucking Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Shit! Shit! Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:43.37,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Once... let's do it just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.87,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,One in six... a one-in-six chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.76,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:06.95,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Here, right now, I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.32,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The way this feels...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami Yumeko, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll let you pay me back in full...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.71,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That really cut it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:36.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Becoming a pet might be even more dangerous for women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:39.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I have to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:43.35,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, where do you plan on gambling next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.51,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A leaflet that was handed out in the hallway just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A notice for the 'Debt Adjustment Assembly'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:57.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just do your best and brush up on your man-pleasing skills, ‘kay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What gamble are we gonna do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.49,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's all good as long as you win, \Nbut losing’s gonna be hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.50,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should drop out after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:16.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ladies and Gentlemen, welcome to the 'Debt Adjustment Assembly'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:19.01,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I am the secretary of the Student Council, Igarashi Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:25.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,In our academy, people who lose their heads over their debts appear every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Thus, the Student Council prepared something \Nto help those in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That would be... the ‘Debt Replacement Game’!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You will gamble in groups of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:39.04,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The debts can be changed drastically according to the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:43.57,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If you come in first, you’ll exchange your debt with the lowest debt of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The lowest with the highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The debt will be replaced, to put it simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The one with the least amount of debt gains nothing, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That’s certainly not the case. For them, the debt will be erased completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:03.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone. This is your second chance. \Nplease make use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.39,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Damn hypocrites…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Quite the lavish proposal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.95,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Could the Student Council be gaining something from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:13.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.19,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I heard you majorly lost against the Council after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I was careless, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I see you decided to participate in this meeting as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Whose fault do you think all of this is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.92,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Come now, no need for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Aren't we friends from the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.33,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,So annoying...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I will now begin distributing \Nthese blank forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:42.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please write down the name of your creditor and the amount owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:49.39,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Most of you are Crowd Debtors, which means that you owe a debt to a non-singular entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Anyone would be overwhelmed by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.48,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Through this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:57.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,may you unify your debt with the Student Council and aim for a second chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.61,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,They're just returning \Nwhatever exploited money
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:03.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,they have to desperate students and get thanked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There's no limit to how thick those masks of theirs are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's more likely that the Council's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.07,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now, I will announce the decided pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Group A. \Nfirst Year, Flower Class - Mozu Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:22.14,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I heard she has a total debt of 310,000,000. {2,800,000 Usd}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to end up in the same group as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.64,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Second Year, \Nflower Class - Jabami Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Second Year, \Nflower Class - Saotome Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:33.23,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Saotome-san, I'll place myself in your capable hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.73,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Ah, shit! \Nam I cursed by her or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now then, let us move to the details of this gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.68,Tln,,0,0,0,,Tln: Indian Poker also known as Blind Man's Bluff
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The game we have prepared for you today is \Ntwo-Piece Indian Poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.84,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The rules are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:50.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You will be using a deck with forty cards, \Nhaving excluded all Joker and Face Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:56.39,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Initially the dealer will deal out the first cards, so be sure to inspect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.48,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Following that, the second card will be dealt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:03.50,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You will avert your eyes from it and \Nplace it in front of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.63,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A Public Card and a Private Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.34,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You will be playing with a combination of these two cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:11.88,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The strongest is a 'Pair', \Ncomposed of two matching numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.61,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Right below that is the 'Mark', \Ncomposed of two matching markings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The weakest is the 'Pig', \Ncomposed of a pair where neither matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:18.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Should two matching types
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,face each other, the one with the larger total sum is deemed the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:25.53,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And this is where the \Ngame becomes interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:29.66,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We will distribute various chips with differing colours, there being ten of each.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:34.14,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The total amount of one's chips is of little importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:38.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This is because in the end, the total worth decides the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:43.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The worth of each chip amounts to a tenth of the player's written debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:47.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Should the debt be 100,000,000 Yen, the chip will be worth 10,000,000 Yen. {900,000, the chip will be worth 10,000,000 Yen. 90,000 Usd}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.32,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The game shall constitute ten turns for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:53.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,For each turn, a payment of one chip must be issued.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.89,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,To add to that, only up to five chips may be placed for each turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:15:00.01,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A single one of my chips would be worth 5,000,000 Yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.59,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,In contrast, one of Yumeko's chip would be 31,000,000 Yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.76,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Just how will this gap influence us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:09.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We will not offer any advice for this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:12.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That applies to cheating as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.41,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,In a world of loss and victory, the fault lies with the deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You will be stopped upon being discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:22.32,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,However, this does not mean that all past actions will be invalidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This concludes our explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I pray you will all do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Well then, should we move along as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:37.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This is the last thing I wanted to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami-san. \Na quick word, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We've been awaiting your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.45,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You'll be the dealer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.48,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This table will have the largest opening gap, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:56.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We can't let there be any mistakes, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.12,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have a connection, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,A coincidence, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Kiwatari-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Where's your Livestock Tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.89,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What, weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.72,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The debts here are just personal statements, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:17.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'm not even close to livestock; \NI just said that I owe a buddy some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:21.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That way, the Council pays that buddy about \N10,000,000 Yen to shoulder that debt. {90,000 Usd}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:25.88,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,So if I win here and get discharged with a refund, I can cash in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's quite confident of you, despite there being a chance of owing a real debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:31.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I've won at three of these meetings before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.36,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There's no way in Hell I can lose to livestock like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.47,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's like picking up dropped cash, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This guy's way too brazen in front of the Student Council...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Looking the other way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Something like this could end up as a huge loss for the Student Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:53.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,but it's still just a self-proclamation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:17:00.18,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now, we will have you commence a \Ngame of Two-Piece Indian Poker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:03.06,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please give your participation fee first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:07.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Once you have inspected your cards, please lay them face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.48,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,As for these, please avoid looking at them and place them facing the top of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.77,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Now then, Kiwatari-sama may begin as the dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:17.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Let's see, what to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:23.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Backing down from the start's no fun. \Nbet! Kiwatari, one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I call. \Ntsubomi, one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.88,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The lower the cost, the lower the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:35.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Going the greedy route would be correct, \Nbut we can't afford to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We have to be careful and–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I call! \Njabami, one chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.44,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:42.65,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Do you even realise how much a chip of yours is worth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Backing down from the start wouldn't make \Nfor an interesting match, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:48.60,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'd have to place bets eventually anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.27,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, but that's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.98,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I like it. Strong-willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.91,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Is she even right in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:56.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.68,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Proclamations have been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please show your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Seven and eight. \N'pig', correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Three, six. 'Pig'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Three, NIne. Mark'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I win this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:13.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Kiwatari-sama wins the round. \Nall placed chips go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.74,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's what you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.26,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We will begin with the second turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.76,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,The dealer role moves to Tsubomi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Bet. \Ntsubomi, one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:26.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.35,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I raise. \Nkiwatari, four chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.36,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:37.15,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,All participants barring Kiwatari-sama fold. \Nkiwatari-sama wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Don't you guys think you're too weak for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This is exactly why you turned to livestock, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:47.33,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Fucking pip-squeaks aren't even a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We will commence the third turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:56.14,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I seem to have drawn quite the card. I'll bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.21,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami, one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Heh. Finally picking up on the challenge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I raise. \Nkiwatari, two chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:07.75,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh, just two? I may be paraphrasing, \Nbut 'are you too weak for this'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please, it's fine. \NIt's called 'strategy'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:15.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll chew up and spit out those molehill chips of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:18.36,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Won't even stand to look at them when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:24.37,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, those chips of yours are plain security for me. There's no way in Hell I'm risking those.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.81,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Then I have no choice but to steal this victory, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.37,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I raise. \Njabami, three chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:31.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Wha–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Interestin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I call. \Nkiwatari, two pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.97,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Proclamations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Please show your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Luck's on my side, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Two and five. \Na 'Mark'!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.31,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.01,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I happen to be confident in my own luck, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.40,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Four and Ten. \N'mark'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.30,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.13,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,We shall now commence the fourth turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.45,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Saotome-sama will deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:09.69,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's just like Yumeko said. \NI have to place a bet eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.33,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.54,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I bet. \Nsaotome, one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.04,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I call. \Nkiwatari, one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:16.79,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.08,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Kiwatari, one chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:23.76,Think,,0,0,0,,If I lose here, my life's going to end up like that ridiculous life plan form said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.92,Think,,0,0,0,,I'll get married to some politician, bear his children, and be some diet trophy wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.27,Think,,0,0,0,,The husband climbs the ladder\N all the way to Minister of Education...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:34.51,Think,,0,0,0,,Our three kids would become independent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:40.04,Think,,0,0,0,,and I'd spend my old age with my husband surrounded by beloved children and grandchildren and no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.63,Think,,0,0,0,,I'd live a long happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:45.24,Think,,0,0,0,,Saotome Mary would reach \Nthe utmost happiness as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:48.74,Think,,0,0,0,,She will lead a life where \Nshe couldn't even begin to wish for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:51.80,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That's worth shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:57.02,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I decide my own life! I'm not leaving it to anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll get back my own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I raise! \Nsaotome, three chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:03.67,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What are you, a moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:10.03,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd just get cold feet and fold after adding that to Yumeko's bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:12.78,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,If I win here, you'll just have two chips left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,There's no coming back from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Like I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.58,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I can see right through livestock like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:24.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Saotome, Yumeko... \Nyou're in this together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.86,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're way too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:30.22,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,In this game, you only know what card you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.95,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,No matter what huge numbers come your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:35.87,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,you'll just lose to the one-in-four chance of there being a 'Mark'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:38.90,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I seem to have drawn quite the card.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Who the Hell even says that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:46.88,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Betting 155,000,000 Yen on an off chance is even more ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.56,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,And that just makes it easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:53.24,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,You just bet that because you knew you had a 'Mark'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:55.38,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It's obvious you're just playing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:56.85,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,That sucks for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:22:01.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Whatever fucking livestock does is always gonna be seen through by us humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.27,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I fold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.39,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Jabami-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:06.28,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:11.10,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Good. They've lost two pairs they could've used.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:14.25,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,At this rate, winning'll be a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:15.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Pretty sharp, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:16.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.91,0:22:21.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Doing heinous deeds all the time must mean you become sensitive to this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:27.17,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Regardless, I'm glad I placed my bet. \Nreally dodged a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:29.05,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What are you even–
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:39.02,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,It was a {\i1}'Pig'{\i0}, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:10.52,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:12.93,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Having cheating makes it quite interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:13.36,Kakegurui - Up,,0,0,0,,... It is merely a means to seize victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:15.46,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,I won with just a 'Pig'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.82,0:24:18.12,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,This match has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:21.00,Kakegurui,,0,0,0,,Devolved to a war of bluffs!
